1
00:01:30,930 --> 00:01:35,020
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:39,460
[2024]

3
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,580
Xia Xiaolan, you must be home.

4
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:09,169
Have the business trip field study report

5
00:02:09,310 --> 00:02:10,560
ready for me

6
00:02:10,750 --> 00:02:11,750
by 10 AM tomorrow.

7
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,190
Home isn't a container,

8
00:02:14,910 --> 00:02:16,040
but a relationship.

9
00:02:17,030 --> 00:02:18,910
We think it will last forever,

10
00:02:19,710 --> 00:02:21,400
but at some stage in life,

11
00:02:21,630 --> 00:02:22,420
we lose it.

12
00:02:24,150 --> 00:02:25,010
Starting then,

13
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:26,710
going home

14
00:02:27,579 --> 00:02:29,350
becomes a new life lesson.

15
00:02:32,329 --> 00:02:34,670
[Episode 6: What Is a Home?]

16
00:02:35,750 --> 00:02:36,560
Actually, I think

17
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,680
today went well.

18
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,470
You paid her back.

19
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:41,870
You don't owe her anything anymore.

20
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,010
Come on down, comrades.

21
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,080
Sorry. Sorry.

22
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:16,470
Please excuse me.

23
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,640
These three

24
00:03:18,870 --> 00:03:20,190
were sent by the county

25
00:03:20,470 --> 00:03:22,400
as agriculture technical guides.

26
00:03:22,630 --> 00:03:24,240
Let's give them a warm welcome.

27
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,000
Amazing!

28
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:26,470
Great!

29
00:03:26,590 --> 00:03:27,150
Welcome.

30
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,470
Hello everyone, I'm Yang Jiancong.

31
00:03:30,470 --> 00:03:31,520
I'm from Guangdong.

32
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,560
Welcome.

33
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,560
Hello everyone.

34
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,710
I'm Wang Jianhua

35
00:03:35,810 --> 00:03:36,810
from the capital.

36
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:37,360
I hope

37
00:03:37,430 --> 00:03:38,680
I can be of help to you all.

38
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,280
Great!

39
00:03:39,310 --> 00:03:40,630
Welcome.

40
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,840
I'm Tan Xihao.

41
00:03:44,030 --> 00:03:45,030
I'm from Jiangxi.

42
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,470
Good!

43
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,480
In the future,

44
00:03:49,910 --> 00:03:50,590
if anyone has

45
00:03:50,590 --> 00:03:52,030
questions about agriculture,

46
00:03:52,030 --> 00:03:53,030
you can ask them.

47
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:55,800
That's great.

48
00:03:57,170 --> 00:03:58,370
Comrade Xia Xiaolan,

49
00:03:59,079 --> 00:04:00,940
I hope this letter finds you well.

50
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:02,360
It's been over 3 months

51
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,590
since we met.

52
00:04:04,590 --> 00:04:07,050
I have some thoughts
I want to share with you.

53
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:10,520
I still remember
the first day I came here;

54
00:04:10,870 --> 00:04:12,590
the first person I saw

55
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,030
was you.

56
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:17,120
Since then,

57
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:20,560
I have believed in fate.

58
00:04:55,190 --> 00:04:56,760
[To: Xia Xiaolan]

59
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,159
Someone is up late,

60
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:41,090
trying to steal the Door God's job.

61
00:05:42,070 --> 00:05:43,600
What are you talking about?

62
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:45,040
Listen.

63
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:47,130
Your uncle is amazing.

64
00:05:48,430 --> 00:05:49,630
Tao isn't bad either.

65
00:05:52,070 --> 00:05:53,070
Tell me the truth.

66
00:05:53,950 --> 00:05:55,240
Just now at dinner,

67
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,040
did you pray to God

68
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:57,750
for rain?

69
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,010
I swear to Chairman Mao.

70
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,020
This has nothing to do with me.

71
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:05,720
Fine.

72
00:06:06,870 --> 00:06:07,960
Since you can't sleep,

73
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,560
let me share a story with you.

74
00:06:12,130 --> 00:06:13,720
Otherwise, if I read it alone,

75
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,210
you might think I rejected you

76
00:06:15,210 --> 00:06:17,070
because I can't let go of the past.

77
00:06:23,870 --> 00:06:25,160
Comrade Xia Xiaolan,

78
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:27,690
I hope this letter finds you well.

79
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,160
It's been over 3 months

80
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,510
since we met.

81
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:33,480
I have some thoughts to share with you.

82
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:36,450
I still remember
the first day I came here;

83
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:38,510
the first person I saw

84
00:06:39,190 --> 00:06:39,920
was you.

85
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:41,920
Since then,

86
00:06:42,510 --> 00:06:44,950
I have believed in fate.

87
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,190
What do you think?

88
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:50,070
Surprised?

89
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:52,570
Wang Jianhua is quite affectionate.

90
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:55,159
He might have been sincere at first.

91
00:06:55,630 --> 00:06:56,390
But later,

92
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,920
he probably just craved

93
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:01,170
the satisfaction he got from you.

94
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,530
Tell me then.

95
00:07:07,870 --> 00:07:08,390
I was

96
00:07:08,390 --> 00:07:10,120
a girl as poor as a church mouse,

97
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:10,800
with no degree

98
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,720
and no job.

99
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,830
As for him,

100
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,920
Once his father was reinstated,

101
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:18,730
he'd be
a university professor's son again.

102
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,570
What did he want from me?

103
00:07:20,750 --> 00:07:22,080
How nice you were to him.

104
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,260
He wanted your sincerity.

105
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:25,160
He wanted your willingness

106
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,820
to help him however you could.

107
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,600
He was never

108
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,600
a good person to begin with.

109
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:31,260
And he had even less hope here.

110
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,390
It was your devotion

111
00:07:32,390 --> 00:07:33,600
that made him feel

112
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,920
he still had value

113
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:36,870
and was still worthy of love.

114
00:07:39,390 --> 00:07:40,430
Zhou Cheng

115
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:42,159
understood this,

116
00:07:43,060 --> 00:07:44,560
but that silly girl who ran into a tree

117
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,750
didn't.

118
00:07:47,070 --> 00:07:48,000
Her devotion

119
00:07:48,230 --> 00:07:50,090
didn't earn her the same respect.

120
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,510
It only built up a mediocre man's

121
00:07:52,730 --> 00:07:54,000
false confidence.

122
00:07:56,830 --> 00:07:57,480
Why...

123
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,930
Wh-Why are you looking at me like that?

124
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,000
It takes a man

125
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,680
to know a man.

126
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,070
Xiaolan,

127
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:06,270
don't joke like that.

128
00:08:06,510 --> 00:08:07,160
I hate people

129
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,820
like Wang Jianhua the most...

130
00:08:08,950 --> 00:08:09,920
Keep it down.

131
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:11,800
Sit, sit.

132
00:08:12,310 --> 00:08:14,040
I won't joke like that anymore.

133
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:18,470
By the way,

134
00:08:19,270 --> 00:08:20,130
why do you think

135
00:08:20,830 --> 00:08:21,560
Xia Ziyu

136
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:23,310
wants you back in the Xia family?

137
00:08:23,310 --> 00:08:25,510
Isn't she afraid you'll cause trouble?

138
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,390
She thinks

139
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,270
I'm still that silly girl

140
00:08:28,270 --> 00:08:29,360
from before.

141
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,570
Enthusiastic, impulsive,

142
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,059
acting without thinking.

143
00:08:33,510 --> 00:08:34,240
She probably feels that

144
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,700
if I stay in the Xia family,

145
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,460
she can control me better.

146
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,260
With so many eyes on me,

147
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,240
it'd be hard for me

148
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,630
to steal her thunder.

149
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:48,240
What a rotten person.

150
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,870
Every time you talk about yourself,

151
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:55,080
it feels like

152
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:57,080
you're talking about someone else.

153
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,260
Because

154
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:01,080
for me, those things

155
00:09:01,510 --> 00:09:02,440
are long past.

156
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,480
I don't want to live

157
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,320
in a fog like before.

158
00:09:07,870 --> 00:09:08,960
I want to start over

159
00:09:09,630 --> 00:09:11,230
and live life to the fullest.

160
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:14,560
Well said.

161
00:09:17,030 --> 00:09:18,320
Seeing Xia Ziyu today,

162
00:09:19,390 --> 00:09:20,240
she clearly has so many

163
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,040
dark thoughts

164
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,970
and has done such shady things.

165
00:09:23,390 --> 00:09:24,840
Yet on the surface, she pretends

166
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,900
to be kind and weak.

167
00:09:26,910 --> 00:09:28,200
She backed down today,

168
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:30,030
but who knows what dirty tricks

169
00:09:30,030 --> 00:09:31,600
she'll have in the future.

170
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,470
Yeah.

171
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:34,970
Even a tiny fly is annoying

172
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,320
if it keeps

173
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:37,840
buzzing around.

174
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:40,790
Xiaolan,

175
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:43,360
my school is collecting

176
00:09:43,510 --> 00:09:45,170
desired major applications.

177
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,030
I plan

178
00:09:47,390 --> 00:09:48,120
to study law.

179
00:09:53,150 --> 00:09:54,390
What I want to say is,

180
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,240
no matter how

181
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,630
Xia Ziyu provokes you,

182
00:09:57,630 --> 00:09:58,760
don't be impulsive.

183
00:09:59,150 --> 00:10:00,320
Don't think about using violence

184
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,380
to solve problems.

185
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:02,670
Trust the law.

186
00:10:03,030 --> 00:10:04,960
Protect yourself and your family.

187
00:10:07,390 --> 00:10:08,550
I know. Thank you.

188
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:16,000
You're so young,

189
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,760
yet you've been through so much.

190
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,580
Are you afraid?

191
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,480
Afraid?

192
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:25,720
Maybe not.

193
00:10:26,910 --> 00:10:27,960
I just don't want

194
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:31,120
to worry these people.

195
00:10:35,380 --> 00:10:36,240
I'm not afraid.

196
