213
00:11:21,790 --> 00:11:23,000
Welcome to shop!

214
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:23,360
Great!

215
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,360
Welcome!

216
00:11:24,390 --> 00:11:25,030
Welcome!

217
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:27,000
Take a look, everyone.

218
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,120
Great prices!

219
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:29,510
Affordable clothes,

220
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:29,960
and very stylish!

221
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:30,870
These are all new.

222
00:11:30,870 --> 00:11:32,030
Fresh from the warehouse.

223
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:33,290
Take a look, everyone.

224
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,360
This outfit is the trendiest

225
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,690
in Longcheng right now.

226
00:11:40,270 --> 00:11:41,200
How much is this?

227
00:11:41,630 --> 00:11:42,960
Let me check.

228
00:11:44,520 --> 00:11:45,320
Yes?

229
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,240
Can you

230
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,510
get this in my size?

231
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:48,680
This one, right?

232
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:49,150
Yes.

233
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:51,840
This should fit.

234
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:53,630
I quite like it.

235
00:11:53,630 --> 00:11:55,870
But my thighs are a bit thick.

236
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,870
Do you think I should pair it with a skirt

237
00:11:57,870 --> 00:11:59,000
or pants?

238
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,600
Pants.

239
00:12:02,630 --> 00:12:03,440
Pants...

240
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,280
What's wrong?

241
00:12:04,790 --> 00:12:06,600
I have thick legs.

242
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,110
I don't know if it'd go with a skirt...

243
00:12:08,110 --> 00:12:08,480
Miss,

244
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:09,750
your legs aren't thick at all.

245
00:12:09,750 --> 00:12:10,320
I think skirts

246
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,360
and pants both suit you.

247
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,860
If you're really self-conscious,

248
00:12:12,860 --> 00:12:14,150
you can get a skirt.

249
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:15,440
As for skirts,

250
00:12:15,550 --> 00:12:17,030
this one actually goes well with it.

251
00:12:17,030 --> 00:12:17,600
But...

252
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:18,600
I think

253
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:20,000
pants work too.

254
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:20,720
Look here.

255
00:12:21,150 --> 00:12:22,000
We have these

256
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,320
jeans.

257
00:12:23,550 --> 00:12:24,480
They're high-waisted.

258
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:25,750
They'll definitely make you look slim.

259
00:12:25,750 --> 00:12:26,600
You can try them all on.

260
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,960
If you don't like them, no pressure.

261
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,030
If you like them, buy them all.

262
00:12:29,030 --> 00:12:29,480
Okay.

263
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,360
I'll try them all.

264
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:30,760
Right.

265
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:32,080
The fitting room is over there.

266
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:32,470
Okay.

267
00:12:32,510 --> 00:12:33,370
Take your time.

268
00:12:35,270 --> 00:12:35,910
Xiaolan,

269
00:12:36,550 --> 00:12:37,120
I...

270
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:38,000
It's okay.

271
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,550
Mom, don't be nervous.

272
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:42,250
Ma'am, come here for a sec.

273
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:42,850
Coming.

274
00:12:43,930 --> 00:12:44,550
Do you have

275
00:12:44,550 --> 00:12:45,480
another size for this shirt?

276
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:46,840
Let me check for you.

277
00:12:58,750 --> 00:12:59,840
Shopping for clothes?

278
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:01,550
Your outfit looks pretty good.

279
00:13:01,550 --> 00:13:03,080
No, mine's pretty nice too.

280
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,100
Let's chat!

281
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:04,910
Hey!

282
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,200
No fun.

283
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:16,550
Fen.

284
00:13:16,990 --> 00:13:17,910
Stop working so hard.

285
00:13:17,910 --> 00:13:18,960
There are no customers anyway.

286
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:19,690
Take a break.

287
00:13:20,390 --> 00:13:21,790
Styling is my weak point.

288
00:13:21,790 --> 00:13:23,030
I need to study and practice more.

289
00:13:23,030 --> 00:13:24,630
Just in case someone comes in.

290
00:13:24,630 --> 00:13:25,150
Fen.

291
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:26,030
Look.

292
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:27,340
Those two guys,

293
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,120
they just squat by our door.

294
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:30,850
The customers dare not come in.

295
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,750
Business used to be good.

296
00:13:33,270 --> 00:13:34,600
Are they intentionally

297
00:13:34,630 --> 00:13:35,560
messing with us?

298
00:13:36,030 --> 00:13:36,930
-Ladies.
-Hey, pretty.

299
00:13:36,930 --> 00:13:37,840
Came to buy some clothes?

300
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:38,790
Wanna grab a bite?

301
00:13:38,790 --> 00:13:39,650
Don't run away!

302
00:13:39,670 --> 00:13:40,960
Look, you scared them away.

303
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:41,620
Seriously.

304
00:13:41,790 --> 00:13:43,670
Ma'am, hope business is booming.

305
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:48,280
Dirty hooligans.

306
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,000
Pretty lady,

307
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,200
looking for clothes?

308
00:14:00,790 --> 00:14:01,510
Don't go.

309
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:03,550
Wanna go on a date?

310
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:04,150
Look,

311
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,750
you scared them away.

312
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:07,960
Bro,

313
00:14:08,630 --> 00:14:09,670
this job is great.

314
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:11,720
We can just bask in the sun,

315
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:12,650
check out girls,

316
00:14:13,030 --> 00:14:14,430
and make some easy money.

317
00:14:15,510 --> 00:14:17,170
How much longer can we do this?

318
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:19,270
Our boss said,

319
00:14:19,510 --> 00:14:21,000
as long as she doesn't say stop,

320
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,840
we can do this every day.

321
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:27,720
What are you doing?

322
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:28,520
Are you crazy?

323
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:30,030
-What are you doing?
-Tossing water and cleaning.

324
00:14:30,030 --> 00:14:31,600
It's my responsibility
to keep my storefront clean.

325
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:32,790
Do I need your permission

326
00:14:32,790 --> 00:14:34,120
to clean my storefront?

327
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:35,630
You wench.

328
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:37,720
You did that on purpose, didn't you?

329
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:38,670
Just you wait.

330
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:39,960
Wait for what?

331
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,550
Are you going to get the police

332
00:14:43,550 --> 00:14:44,880
or the security patrol?

333
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:46,910
I'll be waiting right here.

334
00:14:47,100 --> 00:14:48,600
I can't wait

335
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:50,120
to have a chat with the police

336
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:51,720
about vagrants

337
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:54,270
disturbing private businesses.

338
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,680
It's a serious issue.

339
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:57,240
You wanna die?

340
00:14:57,870 --> 00:14:58,670
I'll kill you.

341
00:14:59,120 --> 00:14:59,480
What are you doing?

342
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:01,080
Let's talk this over nicely.

343
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:04,290
What do you two think you're doing?

344
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:05,360
Drinking...

345
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:06,390
We... We're just...

346
00:15:06,390 --> 00:15:07,030
passing by. Just passing by.

347
00:15:07,030 --> 00:15:08,160
Finished drinking?

348
00:15:09,270 --> 00:15:10,630
Are you three ladies all right?

349
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:11,290
We're fine.

350
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:12,340
If you have any trouble in the future,

351
00:15:12,340 --> 00:15:13,550
remember to call the police.

352
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:13,910
Okay.

353
00:15:14,030 --> 00:15:15,390
Thank you.

354
00:15:15,670 --> 00:15:16,870
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

355
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:20,270
It's okay.

356
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:21,090
Don't worry.

357
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:22,240
Let's go.

358
00:15:22,510 --> 00:15:23,360
Seriously.

359
00:15:30,790 --> 00:15:31,320
Fen,

360
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:32,750
Shangdu

361
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,600
is a provincial capital after all.

362
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:36,120
We're strangers there.

363
00:15:36,770 --> 00:15:37,720
What if...

364
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:38,360
Fengmei,

365
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:39,790
I know,

366
00:15:40,550 --> 00:15:41,510
you're afraid those people

367
00:15:41,510 --> 00:15:42,390
will come back for revenge.

368
00:15:42,390 --> 00:15:43,360
Exactly.

369
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:44,600
Look,

370
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:45,870
we drove those

371
00:15:45,870 --> 00:15:47,130
hooligans away today.

372
00:15:47,200 --> 00:15:48,550
But what if they come back

373
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:49,960
and try something else,

374
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:51,750
or play dirty tricks on us?

375
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:54,360
I get scared just thinking about it.

376
00:15:55,150 --> 00:15:56,280
They wouldn't dare.

377
00:15:56,880 --> 00:15:57,640
Those two men

378
00:15:57,670 --> 00:15:59,530
obviously took someone's money.

379
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:02,240
They'll only do
as much as they're paid for.

380
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:03,480
Even if they really

381
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:04,470
dare to try anything,

382
00:16:04,470 --> 00:16:05,200
that's perfect.

383
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:07,270
The police can catch them red-handed.

384
00:16:07,270 --> 00:16:09,200
But those cowards in the Xia family

385
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,200
probably only have the guts to pull

386
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,260
some dirty tricks.

387
00:16:11,270 --> 00:16:13,480
The Xia family sent those two?

388
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:16,200
It must be them.

389
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:17,750
Only they

390
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,530
would want to see my demise.

391
00:16:20,840 --> 00:16:21,840
But don't worry.

392
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:22,810
I have a plan.

393
00:16:23,510 --> 00:16:24,670
In a few days,

394
00:16:24,870 --> 00:16:27,400
they won't have time
to play all these tricks.

395
00:16:41,550 --> 00:16:43,510
Two bowls of rice with toppings!

396
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:47,350
Free refills on rice if it's not enough!

397
00:16:47,390 --> 00:16:48,520
Thanks, Mrs. Huang.

398
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:49,320
Auntie,

399
00:16:49,670 --> 00:16:50,390
here's the money.

400
00:16:50,390 --> 00:16:51,000
All right!

401
00:16:51,910 --> 00:16:52,550
How did you come up with

402
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:53,550
making this rice with toppings?

403
00:16:53,550 --> 00:16:54,910
I've never seen it before.

404
00:16:54,910 --> 00:16:56,630
Business hasn't been great,

405
00:16:56,790 --> 00:16:58,120
so I just came up with it myself.

406
00:16:58,120 --> 00:16:58,720
Is it good?

407
00:16:58,750 --> 00:16:59,350
It's good.

408
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:00,720
Come back often if you like it.

409
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:01,240
Sure.

410
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:02,390
Here.

411
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:03,360
Okay.

412
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:04,270
This is really delicious.

413
00:17:04,270 --> 00:17:04,800
Isn't it?

414
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:06,480
Come back often if you like it!

415
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:07,240
Take care!

416
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:10,720
Xiaolan, you're here.

417
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:11,640
Come, sit.

418
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:13,480
Have a seat.

419
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:14,599
Come here.

420
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:15,650
Let me tell you.

421
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:16,530
Xiaolan.

422
00:17:16,750 --> 00:17:19,000
This rice dish you taught me to make,

423
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:20,640
everyone loves it.

424
00:17:21,270 --> 00:17:22,440
From now on, when you come here,

425
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:23,829
it's on the house. All free.

426
00:17:23,829 --> 00:17:24,790
I couldn't do that.

427
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:25,680
Running a business isn't easy.

428
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:26,790
You have to charge me.

429
00:17:26,790 --> 00:17:27,680
Don't say that.

430
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:29,160
You made my shop so popular.

431
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:30,560
I can't thank you enough.

432
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:31,620
Mrs. Huang.

433
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:32,690
Check, please.

434
00:17:32,690 --> 00:17:33,110
Coming.

435
00:17:33,110 --> 00:17:34,170
It's settled then.

436
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:35,480
Coming!

437
00:17:43,230 --> 00:17:46,310
[Price List]

438
00:17:55,510 --> 00:17:56,160
Hongxia!

439
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:59,920
Come here, I need to tell you something.

440
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:07,640
What is it?

441
00:18:08,310 --> 00:18:09,440
Look, our business

442
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:10,700
isn't doing very well.

443
00:18:11,070 --> 00:18:12,350
Hasn't your mother been saying

444
00:18:12,350 --> 00:18:14,080
she wants to find you a husband?

445
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:16,750
Why don't you take

446
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:17,880
this time to go back,

447
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,240
help out at home,

448
00:18:19,480 --> 00:18:20,830
and learn some skills?

449
00:18:21,480 --> 00:18:22,960
You don't know how to do anything.

450
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:23,960
When you get married,

451
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:25,090
you'll get scolded.

452
00:18:25,880 --> 00:18:27,680
I'm doing this for your own good.

453
00:18:27,680 --> 00:18:28,240
You know?

454
00:18:29,380 --> 00:18:30,320
You mean

455
00:18:30,350 --> 00:18:31,000
you don't want me

456
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,070
to work here anymore?

457
00:18:32,070 --> 00:18:32,310
No—

458
00:18:32,310 --> 00:18:33,000
What about her?

459
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:34,600
Why don't you make her leave?

460
00:18:34,790 --> 00:18:36,310
Watch your mouth.

461
00:18:36,310 --> 00:18:37,510
Keep your voice down.

462
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:41,620
That's my sister-in-law.

463
00:18:41,780 --> 00:18:43,350
The shop belongs to her.

464
00:18:43,650 --> 00:18:44,440
She's the boss.

465
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:45,770
How can I make her leave?

466
00:18:47,550 --> 00:18:48,590
Hey! It's all...

467
00:18:48,830 --> 00:18:50,160
All gone! Seriously!

468
00:18:51,400 --> 00:18:52,000
Ma'am,

469
00:18:52,390 --> 00:18:53,250
I'm not stupid.

470
00:18:53,550 --> 00:18:54,400
I know the boss of this shop—

471
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:55,330
Xia Changzheng!

472
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:57,480
Get the hell out!

473
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:59,030
Who are you?

474
00:19:00,830 --> 00:19:01,960
Have you forgotten?

475
00:19:01,960 --> 00:19:03,440
It's your bro Zhao Yong.

476
00:19:05,070 --> 00:19:06,030
I'm not looking for you.

477
00:19:06,030 --> 00:19:07,160
We're looking for her.

478
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:08,290
She knows who we are.

479
00:19:09,070 --> 00:19:09,480
I...

480
00:19:09,480 --> 00:19:11,160
Hurry up and pay us the money

481
00:19:11,160 --> 00:19:12,070
for blocking the clothing store.

482
00:19:12,070 --> 00:19:13,000
Clothing store?

483
00:19:13,200 --> 00:19:13,590
What?

484
00:19:13,790 --> 00:19:14,750
It's an adult talk;

485
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:15,640
none of a kid's business.

486
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:16,240
Go inside.

487
00:19:16,480 --> 00:19:17,750
Hey, stop pointing, will you?

488
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:18,790
What's wrong with pointing?

489
00:19:18,790 --> 00:19:19,400
Calm down,

490
00:19:19,830 --> 00:19:20,270
bro.

491
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:21,750
This isn't my shop.

492
00:19:21,750 --> 00:19:22,720
Let's talk over there.

493
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:24,200
Don't ruin their business.

494
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,260
Fine, cut the crap.

495
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:27,030
This was agreed upon beforehand.

496
00:19:27,030 --> 00:19:27,720
Pay up.

497
00:19:27,750 --> 00:19:29,070
You really think we're stupid, don't you?

498
00:19:29,070 --> 00:19:29,680
Stop pointing.

499
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:31,350
Let me tell you, before taking the job,

500
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:32,750
we already figured out

501
00:19:32,750 --> 00:19:33,480
your family's messy business.

502
00:19:33,480 --> 00:19:34,210
Understand?

503
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:35,830
What do you mean "someone else's shop"?

504
00:19:35,830 --> 00:19:36,350
This is the shop

505
00:19:36,350 --> 00:19:37,720
you own with Xia Changzheng?

506
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:38,200
Hey...

507
00:19:38,310 --> 00:19:39,030
Shut up!

508
00:19:41,030 --> 00:19:42,720
H-H-Hongbing.

509
00:19:43,720 --> 00:19:44,780
What are you doing?

510
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:46,240
You've got a problem?

511
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:47,110
I... I...

512
00:19:47,750 --> 00:19:48,350
Get lost.

513
00:19:49,350 --> 00:19:49,830
Uh...

514
00:19:50,070 --> 00:19:50,480
Scram!

515
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:51,440
Hey!

516
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:53,480
This really isn't our shop.

517
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:55,200
Let's have a bowl of noodles too.

518
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:55,550
Hey.

519
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:56,680
Don't.

520
00:19:57,370 --> 00:19:57,900
Get lost!

521
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:59,120
Calm down. Calm down.

522
00:19:59,240 --> 00:20:00,240
H-H-Have a drink.

523
00:20:00,590 --> 00:20:01,880
Don't, don't. How about this?

524
00:20:01,880 --> 00:20:03,200
I'll pour you some water, okay?

525
00:20:03,200 --> 00:20:03,720
What?

526
00:20:04,550 --> 00:20:05,610
What are you doing?

527
00:20:06,200 --> 00:20:07,350
When we paid for Xia Ziyu's

528
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:08,500
schooling, we said

529
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,200
we'd share the blessings

530
00:20:10,200 --> 00:20:11,480
and work together.

531
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:13,000
But look at it now.

532
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:14,920
They're making money themselves,

533
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:16,230
living the high life.

534
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:18,590
Yet they didn't even leave
any scraps for your niece!

535
00:20:18,590 --> 00:20:19,240
Exactly.

536
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:21,070
It's simply too much.

537
00:20:21,960 --> 00:20:22,690
I'm going to look for your mother!

538
00:20:22,690 --> 00:20:23,720
-Mom.
-Get out of my way!

539
00:20:23,720 --> 00:20:24,960
-What are you doing?
-Mother!

540
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:25,270
Mother!

541
00:20:25,270 --> 00:20:26,030
Mom is asleep.

542
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:26,490
Mother!

543
00:20:26,590 --> 00:20:28,310
What's going on?

544
00:20:29,030 --> 00:20:29,400
Mother!

545
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:31,350
You've been
rambling on in a panic for ages,

546
00:20:31,350 --> 00:20:33,080
but you haven't made any sense.

547
00:20:33,270 --> 00:20:34,830
Don't rush. Speak slowly.

548
00:20:35,270 --> 00:20:35,880
Mother.

549
00:20:36,200 --> 00:20:37,130
You have no idea.

550
00:20:37,270 --> 00:20:38,600
That eatery in the city,

551
00:20:38,720 --> 00:20:40,840
is run by Eldest Brother
and Sister-in-law.

552
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:41,770
What did you say?

553
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:43,110
They are the owners.

554
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:44,480
Really?

555
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:46,520
Hongbing!

556
00:20:46,830 --> 00:20:47,510
Xia Hongbing!

557
00:20:47,510 --> 00:20:48,110
Hongbing!

558
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:50,000
Xia Hongbing, get over here!

559
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:51,510
Hurry up.

560
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:55,920
Is what she said true?

561
00:20:56,830 --> 00:20:58,510
I don't know if it's true or not.

562
00:20:58,510 --> 00:20:59,790
But I went to

563
00:21:00,160 --> 00:21:01,270
Eldest Sister-in-law's home village

564
00:21:01,270 --> 00:21:02,270
and asked around.

565
00:21:02,270 --> 00:21:03,530
Here is what they said.

566
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:05,160
They said

567
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:07,500
she is incredibly good to her family.

568
00:21:08,750 --> 00:21:10,150
She even pays them wages.

569
00:21:10,350 --> 00:21:11,480
Do you know how much?

570
00:21:11,550 --> 00:21:12,080
How much?

571
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:13,800
It'll scare you to death.

572
00:21:14,310 --> 00:21:15,310
One hundred yuan!

573
00:21:15,790 --> 00:21:16,590
How much?

574
00:21:16,720 --> 00:21:19,720
And that's not counting
the New Year's red envelopes.

575
00:21:21,550 --> 00:21:22,070
My god.

576
00:21:22,790 --> 00:21:23,920
Is what he said true?

577
00:21:24,070 --> 00:21:24,920
It's true!

578
00:21:24,920 --> 00:21:25,310
Mother.

579
00:21:25,310 --> 00:21:26,440
This child doesn't lie.

580
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:27,830
I've seen it several times myself,

581
00:21:27,830 --> 00:21:29,920
Aunt going to the bank to deposit money.

582
00:21:29,920 --> 00:21:31,350
A stack this thick.

583
00:21:31,510 --> 00:21:32,470
It's definitely this thick!

584
00:21:32,470 --> 00:21:33,800
Must be over a thousand.

585
00:21:34,030 --> 00:21:35,430
Isn't that infuriating?

586
00:21:36,510 --> 00:21:38,400
Where are they now?

587
00:21:39,110 --> 00:21:40,750
It seems like debt collectors

588
00:21:40,750 --> 00:21:41,510
are pestering them.

589
00:21:41,510 --> 00:21:42,310
-What?
-What?

590
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:44,510
They are so rich now,

591
00:21:44,510 --> 00:21:46,350
yet people still come to collect debts?

592
00:21:46,350 --> 00:21:47,680
They are obviously playing

593
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:48,610
the victim card.

594
00:21:48,750 --> 00:21:49,240
Mother.

595
00:21:49,360 --> 00:21:50,830
They are obviously fooling us.

596
00:21:50,830 --> 00:21:52,400
She's doing it just for you to see.

597
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:53,660
Just putting on an act.

598
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:56,590
You two,

599
00:21:56,590 --> 00:21:58,480
just go home and get the money.

600
00:21:58,480 --> 00:21:59,270
It's that simple.

601
00:21:59,270 --> 00:21:59,920
All right, all right.

602
00:21:59,920 --> 00:22:00,590
Dagang, Dayong.

603
00:22:00,590 --> 00:22:02,110
We are all bros from neighboring villages,

604
00:22:02,110 --> 00:22:02,590
aren't we?

605
00:22:02,590 --> 00:22:03,640
If you make a scene,

606
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:04,970
others will laugh at us.

607
00:22:05,070 --> 00:22:05,830
That girl from No.1 High School,

608
00:22:05,830 --> 00:22:07,090
isn't she your family?

609
00:22:07,310 --> 00:22:08,070
Why aren't you afraid

610
00:22:08,070 --> 00:22:09,590
of your own family laughing at you?

611
00:22:09,590 --> 00:22:10,030
Hey.

612
00:22:10,240 --> 00:22:10,680
Hey...

613
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,550
Bro, what are you saying?

614
00:22:12,880 --> 00:22:15,110
We are not that kind of people.

615
00:22:15,540 --> 00:22:17,070
Whether you two are that kind of people,

616
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:17,920
don't you have a clue

617
00:22:17,920 --> 00:22:18,880
yourself?

618
00:22:19,240 --> 00:22:19,900
Haven't you

619
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:21,590
seen our shop

620
00:22:21,590 --> 00:22:22,830
this afternoon?

621
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:24,800
Business is really slow.

622
00:22:24,830 --> 00:22:26,090
If business were good,

623
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,790
we would have just paid you.

624
00:22:28,160 --> 00:22:29,240
It's getting late.

625
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:30,510
Following us around

626
00:22:30,590 --> 00:22:31,480
won't help.

627
00:22:31,480 --> 00:22:32,540
Just go back first.

628
00:22:33,210 --> 00:22:33,690
Fine.

629
00:22:33,720 --> 00:22:34,180
Then...

630
00:22:35,590 --> 00:22:36,450
how about this?

631
00:22:36,480 --> 00:22:37,080
One month.

632
00:22:38,790 --> 00:22:40,750
We'll definitely pay you two in a month.

633
00:22:40,750 --> 00:22:41,480
Is that okay?

634
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:42,720
One week.

635
00:22:43,590 --> 00:22:44,550
Just one week.

636
00:22:44,680 --> 00:22:45,110
Hey!

637
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,720
If I don't get the money in a week,

638
00:22:46,720 --> 00:22:48,000
I'll air all your family's

639
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:49,510
dirty laundry.

640
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:52,030
That girl from No.1 High School

641
00:22:52,030 --> 00:22:53,560
is more honest than you two.

642
00:22:54,270 --> 00:22:55,310
That's one week.

643
00:22:55,950 --> 00:22:57,000
If we don't see the money,

644
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:57,680
we'll...

645
00:22:57,680 --> 00:22:58,270
No, no.

646
00:22:58,310 --> 00:22:59,960
You'll definitely see the money.

647
00:22:59,960 --> 00:23:01,790
I keep my word.

648
00:23:01,880 --> 00:23:03,270
I keep my word.

649
00:23:05,270 --> 00:23:05,680
Okay.

650
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:07,760
-Keep your word.
-Thank you.

651
00:23:08,030 --> 00:23:08,480
Okay.

652
00:23:11,790 --> 00:23:12,850
What are you doing?

653
00:23:18,880 --> 00:23:19,880
Isn't that right?

654
00:23:19,920 --> 00:23:20,350
Exactly.

655
00:23:20,350 --> 00:23:20,830
Mom.

656
00:23:23,350 --> 00:23:24,680
The two heroes are back.

657
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:30,440
You two are full of tricks.

658
00:23:32,010 --> 00:23:33,920
Tricking the whole family
into making money for you,

659
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:34,480
right?

660
00:23:35,030 --> 00:23:37,070
Playing dirty tricks,
yet keeping it all to yourselves.

661
00:23:37,070 --> 00:23:38,830
You're so smooth at that.

662
00:23:39,430 --> 00:23:40,540
Let me tell you.

663
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:42,810
I'm not dead yet.

664
00:23:43,350 --> 00:23:45,110
This family hasn't fallen apart.

665
00:23:45,110 --> 00:23:48,120
Every penny you earned before

666
00:23:49,030 --> 00:23:51,070
belongs to this family!

667
00:23:52,010 --> 00:23:52,970
You... You...

668
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:54,150
From today on,

669
00:23:54,830 --> 00:23:55,550
this shop

670
00:23:56,100 --> 00:23:59,100
will be managed by you and Third's wife

671
00:23:59,200 --> 00:23:59,920
together.

672
00:24:06,010 --> 00:24:06,560
Look.

673
00:24:06,590 --> 00:24:09,070
Mom, what are you saying?

674
00:24:09,550 --> 00:24:11,550
Aren't we part of the Xia family?

675
00:24:12,070 --> 00:24:13,400
We listen to you.

676
00:24:13,830 --> 00:24:15,200
But what you just said,

677
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:16,830
does that mean

678
00:24:17,270 --> 00:24:19,070
you want me to hand over the shop?

679
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:21,120
Mom.

680
00:24:21,440 --> 00:24:22,830
If you're worried,

681
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:24,680
let her keep the money with me.

682
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:25,200
Wouldn't that be fine?

683
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:26,460
Then you can rest easy.

684
00:24:26,590 --> 00:24:29,400
That's just moving it
from the left pocket to the right.

685
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:30,030
No, no.

686
00:24:30,480 --> 00:24:31,640
The main thing is,

687
00:24:32,340 --> 00:24:33,830
what does the shop have to do

688
00:24:33,830 --> 00:24:35,230
with Hongbing's family?

689
00:24:36,000 --> 00:24:36,530
Besides,

690
00:24:36,830 --> 00:24:38,160
with all the farm work at home,

691
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:39,960
are we supposed to stop doing it?

692
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:40,880
Wait.

693
00:24:42,000 --> 00:24:43,800
Mom doesn't know the situation.

694
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:46,240
We haven't made any money.

695
00:24:46,590 --> 00:24:47,960
How could we have any savings?

696
00:24:47,960 --> 00:24:48,720
Right, right.

697
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:49,790
You know when we opened the shop,

698
00:24:49,790 --> 00:24:50,440
it was just...

699
00:24:50,440 --> 00:24:51,200
-We…
-We gave free things.

700
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:52,270
-More or less.
-Yeah.

701
00:24:52,270 --> 00:24:52,680
Right.

702
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:54,270
Look how much we gave away.

703
00:24:54,510 --> 00:24:55,640
If we had money,

704
00:24:55,720 --> 00:24:57,030
we would've sent Junbao

705
00:24:57,030 --> 00:24:58,640
to school in the county town long ago.

706
00:24:58,640 --> 00:24:59,040
Right?

707
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:01,400
Mom.

708
00:25:02,350 --> 00:25:03,680
Actually, if you ask me,

709
00:25:04,180 --> 00:25:05,550
you're getting on in years,

710
00:25:05,550 --> 00:25:06,210
aren't you?

711
00:25:06,480 --> 00:25:07,680
We work the land in the village,

712
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:09,410
but how much can we really earn?

713
00:25:09,510 --> 00:25:10,540
Why don't we all

714
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:12,590
move to the county town together?

715
00:25:12,590 --> 00:25:13,110
Right?

716
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:15,010
You can retire there

717
00:25:15,270 --> 00:25:16,750
and keep an eye on the shop.

718
00:25:16,960 --> 00:25:17,920
It would be great.

719
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:18,400
Mother.

720
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:20,960
I think Hongbing is right.

721
00:25:21,200 --> 00:25:23,070
Besides, life is much better in the city,

722
00:25:23,070 --> 00:25:23,720
isn't it?

723
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:25,180
Let's move to the city.

724
00:25:25,750 --> 00:25:26,720
We're also responding to the national call

725
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:28,850
for Reform and Opening-Up, aren't we?

726
00:25:29,270 --> 00:25:30,350
Let's

727
00:25:31,110 --> 00:25:32,240
discuss that later.

728
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:36,750
Right now,

729
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:39,170
the most important thing is...

730
00:25:41,030 --> 00:25:42,880
for you to hand over all the money

731
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:45,080
you've earned immediately.

732
00:25:45,550 --> 00:25:46,350
Dismissed.

733
00:25:47,310 --> 00:25:48,030
But, Mom...

734
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:52,000
Let's go.

735
00:25:52,350 --> 00:25:53,070
Go!

736
00:25:54,310 --> 00:25:55,370
What are you doing?

737
00:26:04,510 --> 00:26:05,240
Tsk?

738
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:06,740
What's with the "tsk"?

739
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:07,890
I'm telling you,

740
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:10,130
if that money gets handed over,

741
00:26:10,160 --> 00:26:11,290
we're through.

742
00:26:11,550 --> 00:26:12,880
I'm going back to my parents'.

743
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:14,200
What are you yelling about?

744
00:26:14,200 --> 00:26:14,640
What about it?

745
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:15,840
Don't be like Liu Fen.

746
00:26:16,350 --> 00:26:17,110
Be like her?

747
00:26:17,550 --> 00:26:19,480
I think Liu Fen did the right thing!

748
00:26:20,110 --> 00:26:21,920
Xia Xiaolan was right.

749
00:26:22,510 --> 00:26:23,550
Your Xia family

750
00:26:23,750 --> 00:26:24,720
is a pit.

751
00:26:25,070 --> 00:26:25,850
A complete pit!

752
00:26:25,850 --> 00:26:26,510
Say that again.

753
00:26:26,510 --> 00:26:27,680
And what if I do?

754
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:28,640
Say it again, and I'll slap you to death!

755
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:30,350
Come on. Hit me!

756
00:26:30,510 --> 00:26:31,000
I will!

757
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:32,740
Let me tell you,

758
00:26:33,030 --> 00:26:33,830
I'm not Xia Dajun,

759
00:26:33,830 --> 00:26:34,590
that coward.

760
00:26:52,310 --> 00:26:53,200
Take care, you two.

761
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:53,830
Thank you.

762
00:26:53,960 --> 00:26:55,020
Please come again.

763
00:26:55,070 --> 00:26:55,680
Goodbye.

764
00:26:56,030 --> 00:26:56,460
Come in.

765
00:26:56,460 --> 00:26:57,090
Welcome.

766
00:26:57,350 --> 00:26:57,950
Come on in.

767
00:26:59,800 --> 00:27:00,640
Take care.

768
00:27:00,670 --> 00:27:01,730
Please come again.

769
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:02,640
Goodbye.

770
00:27:02,830 --> 00:27:03,350
Thank you.

771
00:27:03,350 --> 00:27:04,880
This outfit is on a special sale.

772
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:06,080
You have great taste.

773
00:27:06,110 --> 00:27:06,880
This one is

774
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:08,240
the latest style in Longcheng.

775
00:27:08,240 --> 00:27:10,000
Our shop is the only place
that has it in Shangdu.

776
00:27:10,000 --> 00:27:10,750
No, no.

777
00:27:11,270 --> 00:27:12,510
Just do as you normally do.

778
00:27:12,510 --> 00:27:13,070
Doesn't it look good?

779
00:27:13,070 --> 00:27:13,920
It suits you perfectly.

780
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:14,920
Look how beautiful it is.

781
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:16,050
It really suits you.

782
00:27:16,270 --> 00:27:16,920
It's gorgeous.

783
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:17,640
You want this?

784
00:27:17,640 --> 00:27:18,030
Yes.

785
00:27:18,200 --> 00:27:18,590
Okay.

786
00:27:18,750 --> 00:27:19,240
Then,

787
00:27:19,310 --> 00:27:20,070
I'll set it aside for you.

788
00:27:20,070 --> 00:27:20,440
Try it on.

789
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:21,550
I think this one suits you better.

790
00:27:21,550 --> 00:27:22,000
Okay.

791
00:27:22,270 --> 00:27:23,240
Welcome.

792
00:27:23,270 --> 00:27:24,600
Take your time looking.

793
00:27:24,640 --> 00:27:26,700
Feel free to try on anything you like.

794
00:27:27,110 --> 00:27:27,640
Let's go.

795
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:33,790
Welcome!

796
00:27:34,920 --> 00:27:35,790
Coming, coming.

797
00:27:35,790 --> 00:27:36,830
Welcome.

798
00:27:37,270 --> 00:27:38,510
Same as last time?

799
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:46,270
Fen.

800
00:27:47,350 --> 00:27:48,270
What did you eat

801
00:27:48,270 --> 00:27:49,510
when you were pregnant?

802
00:27:49,510 --> 00:27:50,240
How did you make Xiaolan

803
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:51,510
so smart?

804
00:27:51,920 --> 00:27:53,640
She's a natural at business.

805
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:55,030
That friend she met

806
00:27:55,030 --> 00:27:55,880
in Longcheng

807
00:27:55,900 --> 00:27:56,790
is amazing.

808
00:27:57,350 --> 00:27:59,370
Those stockings
are in such high demand right now.

809
00:27:59,370 --> 00:28:01,240
There aren't many places in Shangdu
that have them.

810
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:02,300
Several customers

811
00:28:02,480 --> 00:28:04,160
who only planned to buy one or two items,

812
00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:05,960
once they heard about the free stockings,

813
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,160
bought several more.

814
00:28:07,350 --> 00:28:09,350
I think her friend's surname is Bai.

815
00:28:09,830 --> 00:28:10,720
I heard she

816
00:28:11,680 --> 00:28:13,030
helped Xiaolan a lot.

817
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:14,160
Fen.

818
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:15,000
There's something

819
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:16,110
we need to discuss.

820
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:18,060
Business is so good right now.

821
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:19,220
In a couple of days,

822
00:28:19,580 --> 00:28:20,640
when Xiaolan takes her exams,

823
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:21,770
will you go with her?

824
00:28:22,110 --> 00:28:23,910
I definitely have to go with her.

825
00:28:24,200 --> 00:28:25,270
I'm just worried you

826
00:28:25,270 --> 00:28:26,870
can't handle the shop alone.

827
00:28:26,880 --> 00:28:28,680
Then we'll just close for 3 days.

828
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:29,350
Right.

829
00:28:29,350 --> 00:28:30,160
It's no big deal.

830
00:28:30,160 --> 00:28:31,200
Her exams are important.

831
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:31,720
Right.

832
00:28:31,790 --> 00:28:33,160
Close for 3 days?

833
00:28:33,550 --> 00:28:34,680
That's shutting

834
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:35,480
the money out.

835
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:36,680
Xiaolan.

836
00:28:37,110 --> 00:28:38,310
It's such an important event.

837
00:28:38,310 --> 00:28:38,920
I can't possibly

838
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:39,850
let you go alone.

839
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,130
I have to be with you.

840
00:28:41,750 --> 00:28:42,960
Uncle will go with me.

841
00:28:43,350 --> 00:28:43,790
Mom.

842
00:28:44,070 --> 00:28:45,030
You and Auntie

843
00:28:45,030 --> 00:28:46,680
just stay here and run the shop.

844
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:47,200
Besides,

845
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:48,640
you can't go in when I'm taking the exam.

846
00:28:48,640 --> 00:28:49,750
You'd just be standing at the gate.

847
00:28:49,750 --> 00:28:50,640
You might as well

848
00:28:50,640 --> 00:28:52,370
earn more money for my tuition.

849
00:28:52,880 --> 00:28:53,960
How could I forget

850
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:54,790
about your uncle?

851
00:28:54,790 --> 00:28:56,080
Let your uncle go with you.

852
00:28:56,080 --> 00:28:56,610
As for us,

853
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:58,370
we'll stay here and make money.

854
00:29:15,510 --> 00:29:15,960
Here.

855
00:29:16,110 --> 00:29:16,640
Xiaolan.

856
00:29:17,240 --> 00:29:19,240
Eat this egg custard while it's hot.

857
00:29:20,070 --> 00:29:20,800
Thanks, Mom.

858
00:29:21,770 --> 00:29:23,570
Rest a bit before studying more.

859
00:29:24,160 --> 00:29:26,640
♪ Let my heart boil ♪

860
00:29:26,070 --> 00:29:26,550
Mom.

861
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:27,830
It's okay, go to sleep.

862
00:29:27,590 --> 00:29:29,890
♪ Are you also the same? ♪

863
00:29:27,830 --> 00:29:29,000
You won't disturb me.

864
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:29,550
I have unfinished work

865
00:29:29,550 --> 00:29:30,680
in the kitchen.

866
00:29:30,840 --> 00:29:32,590
I'll come back to sleep when I'm tired.

867
00:29:32,590 --> 00:29:36,800
♪ Dreams will always shine ♪

868
00:29:37,690 --> 00:29:40,200
♪ There may also be regrets ♪

869
00:29:40,230 --> 00:29:43,980
♪ If you lose something,
be strong ♪

870
00:29:44,350 --> 00:29:46,750
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

871
00:29:47,840 --> 00:29:50,370
♪ The dreams we dream in the daytime ♪

872
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:53,760
♪ Are passionate yet naive ♪

873
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:58,890
♪ Our youth ♪

874
00:29:56,270 --> 00:29:57,270
You must be hungry.

875
00:29:57,270 --> 00:29:58,530
Have something to eat.

876
00:29:59,380 --> 00:30:02,750
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

877
00:29:59,480 --> 00:30:00,750
Keep your head up.

878
00:30:00,920 --> 00:30:02,180
You'll ruin your eyes.

879
00:30:02,780 --> 00:30:06,210
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

880
00:30:03,240 --> 00:30:04,550
Take a break every now and then.

881
00:30:03,890 --> 00:30:05,740
[Xia Xiaolan's way of memorizing words]

882
00:30:04,720 --> 00:30:05,830
Okay, got it.

883
00:30:06,420 --> 00:30:09,200
♪ We never give up ♪

884
00:30:09,820 --> 00:30:13,190
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

885
00:30:13,210 --> 00:30:16,370
♪ Go ahead smiling and never look back ♪

886
00:30:16,390 --> 00:30:19,750
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

887
00:30:19,940 --> 00:30:22,850
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

888
00:30:23,290 --> 00:30:26,450
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

889
00:30:26,670 --> 00:30:32,340
♪ That'd be enough ♪

890
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:28,750
I've basically remembered

891
00:30:28,750 --> 00:30:30,480
how to solve all the problems now.

892
00:30:30,480 --> 00:30:31,280
That's great.

893
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:32,750
I'm prepared.

894
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:50,760
What's wrong?

895
00:30:51,070 --> 00:30:51,830
What are you thinking about?

896
00:30:51,830 --> 00:30:52,630
You zoned out.

897
00:30:53,030 --> 00:30:53,830
Nothing.

898
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:55,720
You seem happy today.

899
00:30:55,720 --> 00:30:56,640
Of course!

900
00:30:57,480 --> 00:30:58,720
My dad got reinstated.

901
00:30:58,720 --> 00:30:59,310
Really?

902
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:00,790
The decision just came down.

903
00:31:00,790 --> 00:31:02,830
He starts
at the Ministry of Education next week.

904
00:31:02,830 --> 00:31:03,400
Ziyu,

905
00:31:03,920 --> 00:31:04,520
our family

906
00:31:04,960 --> 00:31:07,350
has finally
made it through the hard times.

907
00:31:07,350 --> 00:31:07,960
Jianhua,

908
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:09,110
let's find a time.

909
00:31:09,110 --> 00:31:10,640
I want to visit your parents

910
00:31:10,790 --> 00:31:12,650
and congratulate them in person.

911
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:14,400
Sure.

912
00:31:15,030 --> 00:31:16,030
I might have to go

913
00:31:16,030 --> 00:31:17,590
tidy up the old house now.

914
00:31:18,030 --> 00:31:19,290
You stay here and read.

915
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:21,140
Th-Then let me go with you.

916
00:31:23,200 --> 00:31:24,600
It's all physical labor.

917
00:31:24,680 --> 00:31:25,940
Girls can't handle it.

918
00:31:26,350 --> 00:31:27,350
I can do it myself.

919
00:31:27,480 --> 00:31:28,000
You,

920
00:31:28,070 --> 00:31:29,470
just stay here and study.

921
00:31:29,830 --> 00:31:31,360
The exam is more important.

922
00:31:32,240 --> 00:31:32,840
Good luck.

923
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:47,160
First in the prelims?

924
00:31:48,070 --> 00:31:50,730
And she wants to
come to a college in the capital?

925
00:31:52,030 --> 00:31:53,270
Are you still not over

926
00:31:53,270 --> 00:31:54,160
Wang Jianhua?

927
00:31:57,510 --> 00:31:58,110
Next,

928
00:31:59,070 --> 00:31:59,920
we will award

929
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:01,720
the top 3 students in the prelims

930
00:32:02,110 --> 00:32:04,030
scholarships and grants.

931
00:32:05,270 --> 00:32:07,000
Part of a student's good grades

932
00:32:07,160 --> 00:32:08,480
is thanks to the support

933
00:32:08,480 --> 00:32:09,680
and company of their parents.

934
00:32:09,680 --> 00:32:10,310
I suggest

935
00:32:10,780 --> 00:32:11,880
that this scholarship

936
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:13,750
be collected by the parents.

937
00:32:13,960 --> 00:32:15,030
What do you say?

938
00:32:15,480 --> 00:32:16,720
Yes!

939
00:32:17,830 --> 00:32:19,440
Then I'll read the list.

940
00:32:21,790 --> 00:32:23,110
First place in the prelims,

941
00:32:23,110 --> 00:32:24,400
Xia Xiaolan.

942
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:28,110
Xiaolan really did us proud.

943
00:32:28,680 --> 00:32:30,340
Is Xia Xiaolan's parent here?

944
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:32,240
Here! We're here!

945
00:32:33,030 --> 00:32:33,710
Not me.

946
00:32:34,750 --> 00:32:36,160
Liu Fen, they're calling you.

947
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:37,880
-Please come to the stage.
-Xiaolan's parent.

948
00:32:37,880 --> 00:32:38,900
Go get the money, quick!

949
00:32:38,900 --> 00:32:39,760
So many people.

950
00:32:40,070 --> 00:32:41,200
Go on.

951
00:32:41,510 --> 00:32:43,350
We wish we could go up there.

952
00:32:51,110 --> 00:32:51,830
Great!

953
00:32:51,830 --> 00:32:52,830
Don't be nervous.

954
00:33:05,030 --> 00:33:06,090
Congratulations.

955
00:33:06,730 --> 00:33:07,720
Thank you, Principal.

956
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:08,320
Thank you.

957
00:33:12,680 --> 00:33:13,610
Comrade Liu Fen,

958
00:33:14,510 --> 00:33:15,440
it's truly wonderful

959
00:33:15,440 --> 00:33:16,700
that you raised a child

960
00:33:16,750 --> 00:33:17,810
as good as Xiaolan.

961
00:33:17,920 --> 00:33:18,350
Come,

962
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:19,740
say a few words.

963
00:33:19,790 --> 00:33:21,160
Give the other students and parents

964
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:21,760
a pep talk.

965
00:33:22,010 --> 00:33:23,560
No, I'd rather not.

966
00:33:23,590 --> 00:33:24,510
Say a few words.

967
00:33:24,790 --> 00:33:25,400
Mom!

968
00:33:26,270 --> 00:33:27,070
Be confident!

969
00:33:27,270 --> 00:33:28,870
Confidence makes you shine.

970
00:33:30,680 --> 00:33:31,140
Come on.

971
00:33:33,810 --> 00:33:37,080
[All the best to the students of Anqing No.1 High School
for the National College Entrance Examination]

972
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:38,720
Hello, everyone.

973
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:41,240
I am Xia Xiaolan's mother,

974
00:33:42,030 --> 00:33:43,070
Liu Fen.

975
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:44,350
Great!

976
00:33:48,070 --> 00:33:49,510
With the school right across the street,

977
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:50,550
business is quite good.

978
00:33:50,550 --> 00:33:52,210
Students all come here to eat.

979
00:33:52,310 --> 00:33:53,200
It's a prime location.

980
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:53,720
Okay.

981
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:55,310
All right. I'll think about it.

982
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:56,240
If you're interested,

983
00:33:56,240 --> 00:33:57,070
the rent is negotiable.

984
00:33:57,070 --> 00:33:58,200
Okay.

985
00:33:58,220 --> 00:33:59,820
What is there to think about?

986
00:34:00,480 --> 00:34:01,080
All right.

987
00:34:01,830 --> 00:34:02,830
You two saw it.

988
00:34:03,510 --> 00:34:04,770
This is the situation.

989
00:34:05,750 --> 00:34:06,400
We can't run

990
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:07,470
this shop anymore.

991
00:34:08,159 --> 00:34:10,000
We have to transfer it sooner or later.

992
00:34:10,000 --> 00:34:10,929
When you go back,

993
00:34:11,190 --> 00:34:11,590
Dajun,

994
00:34:11,590 --> 00:34:12,920
tell Mom what you saw.

995
00:34:13,590 --> 00:34:14,920
She trusts you the most.

996
00:34:17,230 --> 00:34:17,880
Brother,

997
00:34:18,489 --> 00:34:19,969
you think Dajun is naive,

998
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:21,860
so you want him to fool Mom, right?

999
00:34:22,440 --> 00:34:23,920
Anyway, before I left,

1000
00:34:23,920 --> 00:34:25,090
Mom gave instructions.

1001
00:34:25,090 --> 00:34:27,219
She sent me specifically to watch you.

1002
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:28,230
She knows you two

1003
00:34:28,230 --> 00:34:29,360
like to play tricks.

1004
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:30,760
From now on,

1005
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:31,940
every penny earned

1006
00:34:32,030 --> 00:34:33,159
must be handed over.

1007
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:35,290
What did she say?

1008
00:34:35,440 --> 00:34:37,000
She said we play tricks?

1009
00:34:37,610 --> 00:34:38,679
Is there anyone in our family

1010
00:34:38,679 --> 00:34:39,760
dumber than us?

1011
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:41,920
Besides, do you think transferring a shop

1012
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:43,190
is like selling cabbages?

1013
00:34:43,190 --> 00:34:45,190
How many people asked this morning?

1014
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:47,000
Dajun, you were here.

1015
00:34:47,480 --> 00:34:48,510
Did anyone ask?

1016
00:34:50,540 --> 00:34:51,440
Congratulations to you both.

1017
00:34:51,440 --> 00:34:52,070
Thank you.

1018
00:34:52,070 --> 00:34:53,330
Thank you, Principal.

1019
00:34:54,030 --> 00:34:55,000
Chen Qing!

1020
00:34:58,550 --> 00:35:01,150
Strive to go forward
without fear of hardship,

1021
00:35:01,480 --> 00:35:03,880
succeed in the exams
and bring glory to all!

1022
00:35:04,630 --> 00:35:05,280
Students,

1023
00:35:06,030 --> 00:35:08,030
the college entrance exam
is in a few days.

1024
00:35:08,030 --> 00:35:09,490
Do you have the confidence

1025
00:35:09,630 --> 00:35:11,760
to take on the college entrance exams?

1026
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:14,360
-Yes, yes!
-Yes, yes!

1027
00:35:17,910 --> 00:35:19,710
Why is it so lively in the school?

1028
00:35:20,510 --> 00:35:21,920
It's 3 days from

1029
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:23,480
the college entrance exams.

1030
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:24,800
They're holding a meeting.

1031
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:27,340
Apparently, they notified
the parents and students

1032
00:35:27,340 --> 00:35:28,550
to all come and participate.

1033
00:35:28,550 --> 00:35:30,760
I heard the top students
who did well in the exams

1034
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:31,920
will even get money.

1035
00:35:32,230 --> 00:35:32,920
Money?

1036
00:35:33,030 --> 00:35:33,920
Yeah.

1037
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:34,860
How much money?

1038
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:36,720
Must be several hundred.

1039
00:35:38,070 --> 00:35:39,670
Xia Xiaolan says her grades are good.

1040
00:35:39,670 --> 00:35:41,130
She'll definitely get it.

1041
00:35:41,600 --> 00:35:42,480
Right, Dajun.

1042
00:35:42,510 --> 00:35:44,400
You... You didn't know about this?

1043
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:46,320
You should be participating in it.

1044
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:47,550
Didn't they notify you?

1045
00:35:47,550 --> 00:35:48,350
Yeah, that...

1046
00:35:48,760 --> 00:35:49,820
That shouldn't be.

1047
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:51,210
-You…
-That shouldn't be it.

1048
00:35:51,210 --> 00:35:52,230
Yeah, you're her father.

1049
00:35:52,230 --> 00:35:53,190
She didn't tell you

1050
00:35:53,190 --> 00:35:54,370
something this important?

1051
00:35:54,370 --> 00:35:54,970
Yeah.

1052
00:35:55,030 --> 00:35:56,310
This... This kid...

1053
00:35:56,670 --> 00:35:58,240
Our Ziyu would never do this.

1054
00:35:58,240 --> 00:35:59,590
That's right, definitely not.

1055
00:35:59,590 --> 00:36:00,400
Seriously.

1056
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:04,670
I forgot.

1057
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:06,230
Jianyong from the next village

1058
00:36:06,230 --> 00:36:07,150
made an appointment for this afternoon

1059
00:36:07,150 --> 00:36:08,070
to come see our house.

1060
00:36:08,070 --> 00:36:09,130
Go, go, go quickly.

1061
00:36:09,220 --> 00:36:09,920
Don't delay things.

1062
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:11,360
You guys sit here.

1063
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:20,510
Fen.

1064
00:36:20,730 --> 00:36:22,730
Not only is your daughter amazing,

1065
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:24,820
you as her mother are remarkable too.

1066
00:36:24,880 --> 00:36:25,760
I was so moved

1067
00:36:25,760 --> 00:36:27,280
by what you said.

1068
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:28,150
My legs went weak.

1069
00:36:28,150 --> 00:36:28,760
I don't even know

1070
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:29,710
what I was saying.

1071
00:36:29,710 --> 00:36:30,480
That was so scary.

1072
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:31,740
I couldn't tell at all.

1073
00:36:31,960 --> 00:36:33,020
Xiaolan's parent.

1074
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:33,920
Hello.

1075
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:35,230
Please don't rush off yet.

1076
00:36:35,230 --> 00:36:36,000
Mr. Sun invited you

1077
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:37,000
to his office.

1078
00:36:38,870 --> 00:36:39,910
The principal wants to see me?

1079
00:36:39,910 --> 00:36:40,580
Yes.

1080
00:36:41,160 --> 00:36:42,090
Then go quickly.

1081
00:36:42,290 --> 00:36:43,280
I'll tell Xiaolan.

1082
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:44,840
We'll wait for you at the eatery.

1083
00:36:44,840 --> 00:36:45,190
Okay.

1084
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:45,760
Go ahead.

1085
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:46,290
Let's go.

1086
00:36:47,630 --> 00:36:48,630
Must be good news.

1087
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:53,060
[Anqing No.1 High School]

1088
00:36:51,550 --> 00:36:52,610
Comrade, comrade.

1089
00:36:52,760 --> 00:36:53,670
Who are you looking for?

1090
00:36:53,670 --> 00:36:55,070
I'm looking for Xia Xiaolan.

1091
00:36:55,070 --> 00:36:56,400
What is your relationship to her?

1092
00:36:56,400 --> 00:36:57,260
I'm her father.

1093
00:36:57,590 --> 00:37:00,120
I haven't heard that
Xia Xiaolan has a father.

1094
00:37:00,650 --> 00:37:01,650
Watch your mouth!

1095
00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:02,770
I told your mom

1096
00:37:03,110 --> 00:37:05,000
we'd be at the eatery
in front of the school gate.

1097
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:06,000
She knows, right?

1098
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:06,440
Yes.

1099
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:07,610
That's good.

1100
00:37:08,760 --> 00:37:09,760
Watch your mouth!

1101
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:11,000
You still can't go in.

1102
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:12,600
Wait, what is he doing here?

1103
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:14,530
Xiaolan!

1104
00:37:14,910 --> 00:37:16,590
That's my daughter right there.

1105
00:37:16,590 --> 00:37:17,120
Xiaolan!

1106
00:37:17,550 --> 00:37:18,210
Move aside.

1107
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:19,000
Xia Dajun.

1108
00:37:19,630 --> 00:37:20,700
What are you doing here?

1109
00:37:20,700 --> 00:37:21,630
I am your father.

1110
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:23,110
Can't I come to see you?

1111
00:37:24,150 --> 00:37:26,030
You have the nerve
to call yourself her father?

1112
00:37:26,030 --> 00:37:27,560
Look at how you treated her.

1113
00:37:27,880 --> 00:37:28,840
Shameless!

1114
00:37:30,560 --> 00:37:32,070
I heard there's a meeting inside.

1115
00:37:32,070 --> 00:37:33,280
All the parents are in there.

1116
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:34,360
I'm your father.

1117
00:37:34,560 --> 00:37:35,710
Why didn't you invite me?

1118
00:37:35,710 --> 00:37:36,310
Xia Dajun,

1119
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:38,020
what are you thinking?

1120
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:39,630
You want to be my father?

1121
00:37:39,630 --> 00:37:40,630
Do you deserve to?

1122
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:43,030
You weren't there when I was suffering.

1123
00:37:43,030 --> 00:37:44,440
Now that the hard times are over,

1124
00:37:44,440 --> 00:37:46,040
you want to reap the rewards?

1125
00:37:46,360 --> 00:37:47,500
Dream on.

1126
00:37:48,280 --> 00:37:49,280
Usually, you don't even remember

1127
00:37:49,280 --> 00:37:50,320
that I exist.

1128
00:37:51,880 --> 00:37:53,340
I don't even need to guess.

1129
00:37:53,670 --> 00:37:55,600
Xia Ziyu sent you here, didn't she?

1130
00:37:55,910 --> 00:37:56,790
Ziyu said

1131
00:37:57,420 --> 00:37:58,710
taking you and your mother back

1132
00:37:58,710 --> 00:37:59,910
would be good for you.

1133
00:38:01,090 --> 00:38:02,730
Ziyu said, Ziyu said.

1134
00:38:03,070 --> 00:38:03,800
Xia Dajun.

1135
00:38:04,230 --> 00:38:05,070
Can't you,

1136
00:38:05,070 --> 00:38:05,760
just for once,

1137
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:07,090
use your brain to think?

1138
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:08,900
Look for yourself.

1139
00:38:09,000 --> 00:38:10,030
Am I better off now,

1140
00:38:10,030 --> 00:38:11,360
or when I was in the Xia family?

1141
00:38:11,360 --> 00:38:12,150
Is there anyone in that family

1142
00:38:12,150 --> 00:38:12,820
who wants the best for me

1143
00:38:12,820 --> 00:38:13,820
or my mother?

1144
00:38:14,670 --> 00:38:15,320
Dajun.

1145
00:38:16,150 --> 00:38:16,760
Dajun.

1146
00:38:18,110 --> 00:38:18,640
Xiaolan.

1147
00:38:19,130 --> 00:38:20,280
Well, whatever needs to be said,

1148
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:21,230
let's talk at home.

1149
00:38:21,230 --> 00:38:22,550
There are too many people here.

1150
00:38:22,550 --> 00:38:23,320
Let's go home.

1151
00:38:23,320 --> 00:38:24,680
Talk behind closed doors.

1152
00:38:24,680 --> 00:38:25,360
Right, Brother?

1153
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:25,840
Yes.

1154
00:38:26,070 --> 00:38:26,960
Xiaolan, d-don't

1155
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:28,150
talk here. Let's go home.

1156
00:38:28,150 --> 00:38:29,630
Come on, go back with Auntie.

1157
00:38:29,630 --> 00:38:30,670
What does this have to do with you?

1158
00:38:30,670 --> 00:38:31,960
You haven't finished
your act yet, have you?

1159
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:32,470
Xiaolan.

1160
00:38:32,470 --> 00:38:34,480
You're never done playing along, are you?

1161
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:34,920
Fine.

1162
00:38:35,230 --> 00:38:36,800
Since the Xia family loves acting so much,

1163
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:37,400
all right,

1164
00:38:37,480 --> 00:38:39,360
put on a good show right here today.

1165
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:40,320
With so many teachers

1166
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:41,360
and students here,

1167
00:38:41,360 --> 00:38:42,670
go ahead and put on your act.

1168
00:38:42,670 --> 00:38:43,550
Just act out

1169
00:38:44,030 --> 00:38:46,160
how the Xia family plotted against me,

1170
00:38:46,550 --> 00:38:47,110
and now,

1171
00:38:47,110 --> 00:38:48,370
how you want to ruin me.

1172
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:49,800
I heard you

1173
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:51,760
are still living
at your older brother's house.

1174
00:38:51,760 --> 00:38:53,690
Is there anyone else in that house?

1175
00:38:54,590 --> 00:38:56,000
We can arrange for someone

1176
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:57,150
to accompany her for the exam.

1177
00:38:57,150 --> 00:38:58,800
If you have trouble
with the travel expenses,

1178
00:38:58,800 --> 00:38:59,510
I personally...

1179
00:38:59,510 --> 00:39:00,640
No need, Principal.

1180
00:39:01,030 --> 00:39:02,800
We'll handle the money ourselves.

1181
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:03,960
Thank you, Principal.

1182
00:39:03,960 --> 00:39:04,510
Thank you.

1183
00:39:04,510 --> 00:39:06,070
Mr. Sun! Mr. Sun!

1184
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:09,000
Qi.

1185
00:39:09,630 --> 00:39:11,030
Why are you so flustered?

1186
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:13,000
Xiaolan's father is here.

1187
00:39:17,960 --> 00:39:18,890
What's going on?

1188
00:39:19,030 --> 00:39:20,110
We are all your elders.

1189
00:39:20,110 --> 00:39:21,030
You're

1190
00:39:21,030 --> 00:39:22,360
so rude now.

1191
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:23,840
We all want what's best for you.

1192
00:39:23,840 --> 00:39:24,500
Apologize!

1193
00:39:25,120 --> 00:39:27,380
Who should apologize to whom, Xia Dajun?

1194
00:39:27,550 --> 00:39:29,000
You kept claiming

1195
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:30,000
to be her father just now.

1196
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:31,110
What kind of father

1197
00:39:31,330 --> 00:39:32,590
sides with outsiders?

1198
00:39:32,590 --> 00:39:34,150
Shouldn't you side with your own daughter?

1199
00:39:34,150 --> 00:39:34,880
Am I right?

1200
00:39:35,070 --> 00:39:37,360
-Exactly.
-Yeah. Right.

1201
00:39:37,440 --> 00:39:39,100
How can there be such a person?

1202
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:40,440
Yeah.

1203
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:42,970
Xia... Xia Xiaolan.

1204
00:39:43,400 --> 00:39:44,200
Let me ask you.

1205
00:39:44,580 --> 00:39:45,830
Am I your father?

1206
00:39:45,920 --> 00:39:47,780
Are you coming back with me or not?

1207
00:39:47,840 --> 00:39:48,440
You?

1208
00:39:49,190 --> 00:39:50,230
Who do you think you are?

1209
00:39:50,230 --> 00:39:50,840
You... You...

1210
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:51,700
Say that again.

1211
00:39:51,710 --> 00:39:53,040
Fine, I'll say it again.

1212
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:54,150
Who do you think you are?

1213
00:39:54,150 --> 00:39:55,410
Want me to say it again?

1214
00:39:55,550 --> 00:39:56,030
I...

1215
00:39:56,510 --> 00:39:57,480
What are you saying?

1216
00:39:57,480 --> 00:39:58,320
Xia Dajun!

1217
00:39:58,360 --> 00:39:59,110
I should teach you a lesson!

1218
00:39:59,110 --> 00:40:00,110
Stop! Stop it!

1219
00:40:00,630 --> 00:40:01,360
Liu Fen!

1220
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:02,550
Well said!

1221
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:05,000
Xia Dajun.

1222
00:40:06,710 --> 00:40:07,710
I want a divorce.

1223
00:40:08,880 --> 00:40:09,630
Divorce?

1224
00:40:13,510 --> 00:40:14,840
What are you talking about?

1225
00:40:14,840 --> 00:40:15,700
Say that again.

1226
00:40:16,330 --> 00:40:17,300
Are you deaf?

1227
00:40:17,710 --> 00:40:19,110
Didn't you hear Xiaolan?

1228
00:40:19,440 --> 00:40:20,770
She didn't do anything.

1229
00:40:21,550 --> 00:40:22,880
Yet others bullied her,

1230
00:40:23,190 --> 00:40:25,190
and the Xia family
wants to drive her to death.

1231
00:40:25,190 --> 00:40:26,630
You didn't stand up for her.

1232
00:40:26,630 --> 00:40:27,420
Instead, you joined outsiders

1233
00:40:27,420 --> 00:40:28,500
to pressure her.

1234
00:40:30,000 --> 00:40:32,190
You don't deserve to be Xiaolan's father.

1235
00:40:32,190 --> 00:40:33,050
Let me tell you,

1236
00:40:33,360 --> 00:40:35,230
Xiaolan is not going back
to the Xia family.

1237
00:40:35,230 --> 00:40:36,690
I'm not going back either.

1238
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:37,800
I want a divorce.

1239
00:40:38,630 --> 00:40:39,280
Liu Fen.

1240
00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:40,590
With so many people here,

1241
00:40:40,590 --> 00:40:41,360
aren't you ashamed

1242
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:42,620
of saying such things?

1243
00:40:42,630 --> 00:40:44,430
What's shameful about divorce?

1244
00:40:44,550 --> 00:40:45,280
Everyone has the right

1245
00:40:45,280 --> 00:40:46,670
to pursue happiness.

1246
00:40:47,230 --> 00:40:47,710
Right.

1247
00:40:48,110 --> 00:40:49,510
Divorce isn't shameful.

1248
00:40:50,590 --> 00:40:52,250
Xia Dajun is the shameful one.

1249
00:40:53,510 --> 00:40:54,070
Liu Fen.

1250
00:40:54,630 --> 00:40:55,960
Who gave you the guts?

1251
00:40:56,720 --> 00:40:57,670
You mother and daughter

1252
00:40:57,670 --> 00:40:59,200
are truly a pair of bitches.

1253
00:40:59,480 --> 00:41:00,800
Today, in front of everyone,

1254
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:02,130
I'll teach you a lesson!

1255
00:41:03,230 --> 00:41:04,290
Comrade, comrade!

1256
00:41:15,440 --> 00:41:17,030
I'm telling you, Xia Dajun.

1257
00:41:17,030 --> 00:41:17,960
I'll teach you a lesson today!

1258
00:41:17,960 --> 00:41:18,690
You bastard!

1259
00:41:34,070 --> 00:41:34,840
Get off!

1260
00:41:35,630 --> 00:41:36,190
Stop!

1261
00:41:36,630 --> 00:41:37,690
Stop it, all of you!

1262
00:41:39,920 --> 00:41:40,920
Don't step on me.

1263
00:41:42,670 --> 00:41:43,200
Xiaolan!

1264
00:41:43,590 --> 00:41:44,000
Xiaolan.

1265
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:44,920
Xiaolan! Xiaolan!

1266
00:41:44,920 --> 00:41:46,070
How are you, Xiaolan?

1267
00:41:46,070 --> 00:41:47,510
Where did you hurt yourself?

1268
00:41:47,510 --> 00:41:48,070
Mom.

1269
00:41:49,070 --> 00:41:50,510
I think my hand hurts.

1270
00:41:50,590 --> 00:41:51,280
Your hand?

1271
00:41:51,280 --> 00:41:52,710
Ms. Qi. Send her to the hospital.

1272
00:41:52,710 --> 00:41:53,070
Okay.

1273
00:41:53,070 --> 00:41:53,510
Hurry!

1274
00:41:53,510 --> 00:41:54,070
Be careful.

1275
00:41:54,070 --> 00:41:54,960
Slowly.

1276
00:41:55,510 --> 00:41:56,670
Okay, let's go.

1277
00:41:56,760 --> 00:41:57,630
Hurry up!

1278
00:41:58,360 --> 00:41:59,420
Make way! Make way!

1279
00:41:59,480 --> 00:41:59,880
Hurry!

1280
00:42:11,190 --> 00:42:12,400
Looking at the X-ray,

1281
00:42:12,400 --> 00:42:13,880
there is no major fracture.

1282
00:42:13,880 --> 00:42:15,550
But there is a hairline fracture.

1283
00:42:15,550 --> 00:42:16,210
Right here.

1284
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:19,320
She shouldn't move it for a while.

1285
00:42:19,320 --> 00:42:19,760
Okay?

1286
00:42:20,400 --> 00:42:22,000
We need to put a cast on it.

1287
00:42:23,710 --> 00:42:24,280
Well...

1288
00:42:24,840 --> 00:42:26,400
Can she still write?

1289
00:42:26,840 --> 00:42:28,280
The college entrance exam
is in a few days.

1290
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:30,140
She was 1st in our city's prelims.

1291
00:42:30,360 --> 00:42:31,750
This exam is very important to her.

1292
00:42:31,750 --> 00:42:33,110
You have to help us.

1293
00:42:33,550 --> 00:42:34,750
First in the prelims?

1294
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:37,930
To take the exam for 3 days in the row

1295
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:39,600
will ruin her wrist for good.

1296
00:42:41,280 --> 00:42:41,920
Dajun.

1297
00:42:58,740 --> 00:43:00,540
For her to have such an accident,

1298
00:43:00,630 --> 00:43:01,760
it really is a pity.

1299
00:43:04,550 --> 00:43:05,480
It's all my fault.
